_sText:
The tomb of mighty pharaoh Ramesses has remained hidden for hundreds of years. Within it's walls lies riches of untold wealth. Can you and your associates locate this hidden room?

Beware though. Deciphered hieroglyphs tell us that it is well guarded by many traps and hazzards.

Watch your step!

Due to very popluar demand, this is the thrid and final version.

It now contains 64 ct spawn points, 2 t spawn points, some fixes and some harder traps.
